  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6524027">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6524027/" class="title-link">可以參考的讀物</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6524027"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/56395629/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u56395629-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/56395629/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">鎮長</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-01-24"
      class="main-meta">2014-01-24 11:18:03</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6524027_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  說到石原莞爾這個名字，就筆者本身對他的印象來說，不是很好，我想華人界應該都差不多吧。讀完他這本(其實是兩本合併)著作後，要說改觀嘛，其實也沒有。:P   《最終戰爭論》跟《戰爭史大觀》是石原在二戰期間撰寫的兩本綜合其思想跟研究戰史成果的著作，在當時有其時代意義，引...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6524027/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6524027_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6524027_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





